READMEのヒーロー画像をPowerBook G4 Ti上で動くIllustrator 8.0で制作しました。全てこのTiBookにマウスをつないで2時間ぐらいで作成したものなので、権利等関係なくご自由にお使いください。おまけとして作業風景の写真もつけてあります。

The README hero artwork was created in Illustrator 8.0 running on a PowerBook G4 Ti. Everything here was made on this TiBook with a mouse in about two hours, so feel free to use it however you like. As a small extra, I have also included a photo of the actual work in progress.

Please enjoy!
